        <abstract> 
<p>Continues prior letter of this date. Has received CD’s [<hi rend="doubleUnderline">1202</hi>]. Thanks CD for saving his correspondence.</p> 
            <p>Sent "a yarn about species" in October mail.</p> 
<p>Some "puerile" JDH letters printed in <hi rend="italic">Athenæum</hi>.</p>  
<p>Requests CD extract anything valuable from his letters to CD and Lyell for <hi rend="italic">Athenæum</hi>.</p> 
            <p>CD’s complemental males in barnacles wonderful.</p>
            <p>Warns CD to drop his battle about perpetuity of names in species descriptions.</p>
        </abstract>
